1. Purpose

Purpose of the Thorn is to create a a Pool of temporary grid variable to be used and
shared by various thorn to be used as scratch for doing local computation.
The Thorns that use variables from this pool should assume no consistency.


The name of allocatated array of grid variable is: TempPoolGF


To use this pool of temporary variable one shoud insert in interface.ccl:

> inherits: TempPool 

To use this pool of temporary variable one shoud insert in interface.ccl:

> shares: TempPool
> USES CCTK_INT 
> restricted:
> CCTK_INT Test_maxntemp "Turns on the necessary numbers of temporary variables in TempPool" ACCUMULATOR-BASE=TempPool::maxntemp
> {
>   1:1 :: ""
> } 1
